title: Basic Recent Posts/Pages
description: Show list of pages in reverse order by time.
...

~~~ .php
$_path = PAGE . DS . 'article';
$_chunk = 7;

echo '<h3>Recent Pages</h3>';
if ($_pages = Get::pages($_path, 'page', -1, 'time')) {
    echo '<ul>';
    foreach (Anemon::eat($_pages)->chunk($_chunk, 0) as $_page) {
        $_page = Page::open($_page['path'])->get([
            'url' => null,
            'title' => null
        ]);
        echo '<li><a href="' . $_page['url'] . '">' . $_page['title'] . '</a></li>';
    }
    echo '</ul>';
}
~~~

 - `$_path` → select which page folder you want to list.
 - `$_chunk` → how many pages you want to show in the list.